---
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>JOURNAL // MATTIA VOLPI #77</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syncopate:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root { --blue: #00b4ff; --black: #050505; --dark-gray: #0d0d0d; }
        
        body { 
            margin: 0; background: var(--black); color: white; 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 100% 100%, 60px 60px, 60px 60px;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
        
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

        .journal-header { padding: 200px 0 60px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.1); }
        .tag { font-family: 'Syncopate'; color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        h1 { font-family: 'Syncopate'; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4.5rem); font-style: italic; margin: 15px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -1px; }

        /* --- JOURNAL GRID --- */
        .journal-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); 
            gap: 40px; 
            padding: 60px 0 120px;
        }

        /* CARD IN STILE LOG DI SISTEMA */
        .log-card {
            background: rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 35px;
            position: relative;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Angolino tecnico distintivo */
        .log-card::after {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 20px; height: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--blue); border-right: 2px solid var(--blue);
            opacity: 0.3;
            transition: 0.4s ease;
        }

        .log-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue);
            background: rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.05);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .log-card:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            width: 30px; height: 30px;
        }

        .log-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .log-id {
            font-family: 'Syncopate';
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: var(--blue);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .log-date {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            opacity: 0.4;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .log-card h2 {
            font-family: 'Syncopate';
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .log-card:hover h2 {
            color: var(--blue);
        }

        .log-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin: 0 0 30px 0;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .log-link {
            font-family: 'Syncopate';
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: var(--blue);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .log-link i {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .log-card:hover .log-link i {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        /* --- RESPONSIVE --- */
        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .journal-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; padding-bottom: 80px; }
            .journal-header { padding-top: 140px; padding-bottom: 40px; }
            .log-card { padding: 30px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <Navbar />

    <div class="container">
        <header class="journal-header">
            <span class="tag">Telemetry & Stories</span>
            <h1>PILOT <span style="color:var(--blue)">JOURNAL</span></h1>
        </header>

        <main class="journal-grid">
            
            <a href="#" class="log-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="log-meta">
                        <span class="log-id">LOG // CIV SBK</span>
                        <span class="log-date">20.05.2026</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2>PRIMI TEST UFFICIALI CON BMW M1000RR</h2>
                    <p>I dati raccolti a Misano aprono ottime prospettive. Il feeling con la nuova sella e l'erogazione elettronica del motore BMW promettono un passo gara impressionante.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="log-link">READ DATA PAYLOAD <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="log-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="log-meta">
                        <span class="log-id">LOG // BEHIND THE SCENES</span>
                        <span class="log-date">12.04.2026</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2>PREPARAZIONE ATLETICA: FOCUS TELEMETRIA CARDIO</h2>
                    <p>Come l'analisi dei battiti cardiaci e dei tempi di reazione ridefinisce gli allenamenti invernali in sella al motard. Ogni millisecondo guadagnato conta.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="log-link">READ DATA PAYLOAD <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="log-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="log-meta">
                        <span class="log-id">LOG // PARTNERSHIP</span>
                        <span class="log-date">03.03.2026</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2>FIRMATO L'ACCORDO CON IL TEAM PISTARD</h2>
                    <p>Ufficializzata l'unione strategica per la stagione 2026 nel CIV Superbike. Una sinergia nata per puntare direttamente ai piani alti della classifica generale.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="log-link">READ DATA PAYLOAD <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="log-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="log-meta">
                        <span class="log-id">LOG // MEMORIES</span>
                        <span class="log-date">15.11.2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2>IL PASSAGGIO DALL'EUROPEO MOTO2 ALLA 1000CC</h2>
                    <p>Un bilancio tecnico sul cambio di stile di guida richiesto dalle cilindrate stradali rispetto ai prototipi rigidi della categoria Moto2. Gestione dei pesi e della trazione.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="log-link">READ DATA PAYLOAD <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
            </a>

        </main>
    </div>

    <footer style="padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 255, 0.1); background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
        <p style="font-family:'Syncopate'; font-size:0.55rem; opacity:0.3; letter-spacing: 3px;">
            © 2026 MATTIA VOLPI #77 // DATA LOG TERMINAL
        </p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>